  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>Viennese</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>Bleistein has a Viennese attribute,\n        which presumably means that he has moved from Vienna to\n        Chicago, or that his immediate ancestor has done so.\n        Vienna was, like Venice and Chicago, an important city of\n        trade and the home of many nationalities and races.\n        Presumably this is meant to illustrate Bleistein's\n        mobility, but also to string together Vienna, Venice and\n        Chicago. </font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>History of Vienna</td>\n<td><a href=\"Purgatory_I_DA.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>The City and the Stranger</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Bleistein and Misrepresentation</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Burbank and Bleistein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Viennese Bleistein has a Viennese attribute, which presumably means that he has moved from Vienna to Chicago, or that his immediate ancestor has done so. Vienna was, like Venice and Chicago, an important city of trade and the home of many nationalities and races. Presumably this is meant to illustrate Bleistein's mobility, but also to string together Vienna, Venice and Chicago. reference topics History of Vienna The City and the Stranger Bleistein and Misrepresentation Burbank and Bleistein back to \"Burbank\"",
